    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant investment to be roadworthy. The engine currently has a severe oil leak and an undiagnosed knocking sound, while the transmission shifts roughly between second and third gears. Externally, there is substantial rust along the rocker panels and a large dent in the rear passenger door. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery on most seats and a non-functioning climate control system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, sold as-is with no warranties.",
      "price": 5200.0,
