    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the driver who demands both reliability and refined performance. Meticulously maintained and rigorously inspected, it offers a seamless blend of aesthetic appeal and mechanical soundess. This offering represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that adheres to our exacting standards of quality and roadworthiness.",
      "price": 34500.0,
